---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
description: Friendly servicing, diagnostics, repairs and MOT in Southampton.
bodyClass: page-home
useBookingScripts: true
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-media">
    <img src="/assets/images/mechanic-temp.png" alt="Mechanic in workshop at Nandrews Garage">
  </div>
  <div class="container hero-grid hero-grid-full">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Friendly servicing, diagnostics, repairs and MOT for all model vehicles.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">No jargon. No pressure. Just honest, reliable vehicle care from a local garage people feel comfortable coming back to.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-brand btn-lg" href="tel:{{ site.contactPhoneHref or site.contactPhone }}">Call {{ site.contactPhone }}</a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline-brand btn-lg" href="#book-appointment">Book a service</a>
      </div>
      <dl class="hero-metrics">
        <div>
          <dt>Local garage</dt>
          <dd>Based on Shirley Road in Southampton</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Approach</dt>
          <dd>Honest advice and practical service</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>What we cover</dt>
          <dd>MOT, servicing, diagnostics and repairs</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-panel">
      <p class="hero-panel-title">Why people choose Nandrews</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Friendly and approachable service</li>
        <li>Clear advice without the pressure</li>
        <li>Trusted local garage support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block booking-section booking-section-priority" id="book-appointment">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="booking-shell surface-card">
      <div class="section-heading section-heading-left booking-heading">
        <span class="section-kicker">Book now</span>
        <h2>Choose your service, date, and time.</h2>
        <p id="bookingIntro">{{ site.copy.bookingIntro }}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="alert alert-success d-none" id="appointmentSuccess" role="alert"></div>
      <div class="alert alert-danger d-none" id="bookingError" role="alert"></div>

      <div class="booking-progress" aria-label="Booking progress">
        <div class="booking-progress-step is-current" id="bookingStepService">
          <span class="booking-progress-index">1</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Service and date</strong>
            <small>Start with the vehicle booking basics.</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="booking-progress-step" id="bookingStepTime">
          <span class="booking-progress-index">2</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Choose a time</strong>
            <small>Pick from live weekday availability.</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="booking-progress-step" id="bookingStepDetails">
          <span class="booking-progress-index">3</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Add your details</strong>
            <small>Share contact details to confirm the booking.</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="appointment-layout">
        <section class="appointment-selection surface-card">
          <div class="booking-card-head booking-card-head-stack">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow-label">Step 1</p>
              <h3 class="appointment-panel-title">Pick your service and date</h3>
              <p class="helper-copy">Choose what the vehicle needs, then pick a weekday appointment.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="appointment-panel-badge">Weekdays only</span>
          </div>

          <div class="appointment-selection-group">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="bookingService">Select service</label>
              <select id="bookingService" name="service" class="form-control form-select">
                <option value="">Choose a service</option>
                {% for service in site.booking.serviceOptions %}
                <option value="{{ service }}">{{ service }}</option>
                {% endfor %}
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="appointment-date-panel appointment-date-trigger" id="bookingDatePanel">
              <label for="bookingDate">Select date</label>
              <input id="bookingDate" name="date" type="date" class="form-control">
              <div class="form-note" id="calendarHelper">{{ site.copy.calendarHelper }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="appointment-selected">
            <div>
              <span>Selected day</span>
              <strong id="selectedDateLabel">Choose a weekday</strong>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span>Available slots</span>
              <strong id="availableSlotCount">Select a date</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="appointment-meta-list">
            <li>Monday to Friday appointments only</li>
            <li>30 minute slot spacing during opening hours</li>
            <li>If nothing fits, call the garage directly</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="appointment-slots surface-card">
          <div class="booking-card-head">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow-label">Step 2</p>
              <h3 class="appointment-panel-title">Choose a time</h3>
              <p class="helper-copy" id="guestPricingSummary">{{ site.copy.guestPricingSummary }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="time-slot-grid" id="timeSlotGrid"></div>
          <p class="helper-copy" id="bookingPolicySummary">{{ site.copy.bookingPolicySummary }}</p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="surface-card booking-card booking-details-card is-locked" id="bookingDetailsCard" aria-disabled="true">
        <div class="booking-card-head booking-card-head-stack">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow-label">Step 3</p>
            <h3 class="appointment-panel-title">Add your details</h3>
            <p class="helper-copy" id="bookingDetailsIntro">Select a time slot above to unlock the contact form.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="appointment-panel-badge appointment-panel-badge-muted" id="bookingDetailsBadge">Waiting for a time</span>
        </div>

        <form id="bookingForm" class="booking-form">
          <input id="selectedTime" name="time" type="hidden">

          <p class="booking-form-lock" id="bookingFormLock">Choose a service, date, and time before entering your details.</p>

          <div class="detail-grid">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="fullName">Full name</label>
              <input id="fullName" name="name" type="text" class="form-control" autocomplete="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone</label>
              <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" class="form-control" autocomplete="tel" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email (optional)</label>
              <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="form-control" autocomplete="email">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="vehicle">Vehicle registration or model</label>
              <input id="vehicle" name="vehicle" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Optional">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="notes">Notes</label>
            <textarea id="notes" name="notes" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Tell the garage about warning lights, symptoms, or anything useful to know."></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="price-box appointment-summary-box">
            <div>
              <span>Service</span>
              <strong id="selectedServiceSummary">Not selected</strong>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span>Date</span>
              <strong id="selectedDateSummary">Not selected</strong>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span>Time</span>
              <strong id="selectedTimeSummary">Not selected</strong>
            </div>
            <p>Email is optional, but if you add it we will send a confirmation after booking.</p>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn-brand btn-lg w-100" type="submit" id="bookingSubmit" disabled>Confirm booking</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="section-kicker">Services</span>
      <h2>Garage services people actually look for.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="service-grid">
      {% for service in services %}
      <article class="service-card">
        <img src="{{ service.image }}" alt="{{ service.title }}">
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <h3>{{ service.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ service.summary }}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block section-block-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="section-kicker">Why choose us</span>
      <h2>Professional, reliable and easy to deal with.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="process-grid">
      <article class="process-card">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Honest advice</h3>
        <p>The aim is to explain what needs doing clearly, without making customers feel pressured or talked down to.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="process-card">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Skilled diagnostics</h3>
        <p>From warning lights to sensor issues and harder-to-find faults, the team works methodically to get to the root of the problem.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="process-card">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Fair local service</h3>
        <p>Nandrews is positioned as the kind of local garage people recommend because the work is solid and the service feels straightforward.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block section-block-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-panel">
      <div>
        <span class="section-kicker">Visit or call</span>
        <h2>Need to speak to someone about your vehicle?</h2>
        <p>Call the garage, send a message, or drop by during opening hours. Whether it is a routine service or a fault that needs checking properly, the goal is to make the next step clear.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-brand btn-lg" href="/contact/">Contact Nandrews</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container split-grid">
    <article class="surface-card copy-card">
      <span class="section-kicker">Find us</span>
      <h2>{{ site.addressLines[0] }}</h2>
      <p>{{ site.addressLines[1] }}</p>
      <p>{{ site.serviceArea }}</p>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-brand" href="tel:{{ site.contactPhoneHref or site.contactPhone }}">Call {{ site.contactPhone }}</a>
    </article>

    <article class="surface-card copy-card">
      <span class="section-kicker">Opening hours</span>
      <h2>Open Monday to Friday.</h2>
      <ul class="list-clean">
        {% for item in site.openingHours %}
        <li><strong>{{ item.day }}:</strong> {{ item.hours }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
